data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Nestled within the highly sought-after Villas at Oak Bend community, this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom villa offers 1,357 square feet of luxurious living. Step into a world of sophistication seamlessly paired with contemporary convenience. As you enter, you'll be greeted by pristine laminate flooring that not only exudes elegance but also ensures easy upkeep throughout. The open and airy living spaces are bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for guests and residents. Calling all culinary enthusiasts and entertainers! The kitchen is a true masterpiece with upgraded countertops and soft glow recessed lighting. It's the perfect space to whip up your favorite meals or enjoy a leisurely breakfast. However, the true gem of this home lies beyond the main living areas. Step out onto the rear patio â€“ your oasis. Whether indulging in a good book or savoring an al fresco meal, the fully fenced backyard offers unmatched privacy and serenity. Don't forget the garage! This versatile space is perfect for housing your vehicles, storage, or even setting up a hobby area. This home is situated in a neighborhood renowned for its top-tier schools, gourmet dining options, and easy access to major highways (US-41, US-19, I-275, and I-75). It offers a harmonious blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience. Don't miss your chance to experience an upgrade in lifestyle â€“ secure your exclusive viewing today! Your dream home awaits at the Villas at Oak Bend.
